               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="173002280007"></xptr>The Prisoner deny'd the Fact, pleaded, that there had been since the time that the Prosecutor charged him with the Robbery, an Intimacy between them, that she had been several times at his House, had there drank Coffee, and made his Wife a Mantua , and never charged him with having Robb'd her. He called Evidences who proved it; and upon a full hearing of the Matter, the Jury <rs id="t17300228-14-verdict75" type="verdictDescription">
